{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaSource.sourceBuffers","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/sourceBuffers","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Media_Source_Extensions_API\">Media Source Extensions API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/activeSourceBuffers\"><code>activeSourceBuffers</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/duration\"><code>duration</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>sourceBuffers</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/addSourceBuffer\"><code>addSourceBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/clearLiveSeekableRange\"><code>clearLiveSeekableRange()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/endOfStream\"><code>endOfStream()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/isTypeSupported\"><code>isTypeSupported()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/removeSourceBuffer\"><code>removeSourceBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/setLiveSeekableRange\"><code>setLiveSeekableRange()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Media Source Extensions に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement/getVideoPlaybackQuality\"><code>HTMLVideoElement.getVideoPlaybackQuality()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>TextTrack.sourceBuffer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoPlaybackQuality\"><code>VideoPlaybackQuality</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VideoTrack/sourceBuffer\"><code>VideoTrack.sourceBuffer</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a> インターフェイス の <strong><code>sourceBuffers</code></strong> 読み取り専用プロパティは、この <code>MediaSource</code> に関連付けられた <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> オブジェクトのリストを含む <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code></a> オブジェクトを返します。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>mySourceBuffers</em> = <em>mediaSource</em>.sourceBuffers;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>次のスニペットは、Nick Desaulniers によって書かれた簡単な例に基づいています（<a href=\"http://nickdesaulniers.github.io/netfix/demo/bufferAll.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ライブで完全なデモを見る</a>か、<a href=\"https://github.com/nickdesaulniers/netfix/blob/gh-pages/demo/bufferAll.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ソースをダウンロード</a>してさらに調査してください）。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">sourceOpen</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">_</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//console.log(this.readyState); // open</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mediaSource <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> sourceBuffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addSourceBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mimeCodec<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetchAB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>assetURL<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">buf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    sourceBuffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'updateend'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">_</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">endOfStream</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sourceBuffers<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 上で追加されたソースバッファが含まれます</span>\n      video<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">//console.log(mediaSource.readyState); // ended</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    sourceBuffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buf<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#idl-def-mediasource-sourcebuffers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Media Source Extensions<br><small lang=\"ja\">sourceBuffers の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaSource.sourceBuffers","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/sourceBuffers/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"MediaSource インターフェイス の sourceBuffers 読み取り専用プロパティは、この MediaSource に関連付けられた SourceBuffer オブジェクトのリストを含む SourceBufferList オブジェクトを返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaSource.sourceBuffers","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/mediasource/sourcebuffers","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/mediasource/sourcebuffers/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource","title":"MediaSource"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/sourceBuffers","title":"MediaSource.sourceBuffers"}],"pageTitle":"MediaSource.sourceBuffers - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}